name: Prescott Family Dentistry
overview: Good oral health is a foundation to overall health and well-being. A great smile is a sign of good dental hygiene and can greatly improve your physical appearance and boost your self-confidence. Dr. Prescott is a Fort Mill dentist that is ready to provide solutions ranging from preventive to restorative to cosmetic dentistry procedures to solve all your dental problems. He is one of the topnotch dentists (Fort Mill, SC area) that provide comprehensive dentistry services for the family. Dr. Prescott is one of the best Fort Mill dentists that can provide you any kind of dental service you need, from teeth cleaning to digital x-rays, dental implants, tooth color restoration, root canal treatments, and so much more.
